{"tid":2438381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"詭秘「三指魔爪」壓石澳龍脊 漁護署認衰拆走：同附近自然環境唔夾","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T19:14:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"b46814bd37e9d98b03c19aef485b3f61255d4073","tid":2438381,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"疫情下港人多郊遊散心，欣賞自然景色，若山野環境出現不明建築，實在有礙觀瞻。有行山人士近日在石澳龍脊山頭發現一座疑似「魔爪風水陣」，旁邊有大量木柱包圍，佈局令人不解，不少網民轟「風水陣」大殺風景。《蘋果》今日登上龍脊直擊，發現「魔爪」已被拆下放在一旁，並以帆布遮蓋，而周邊木柱仍在。漁護署承認是始作俑者，現已移除擺設。<br />\n<br />\n綜合記者現場及行山客拍攝到的圖片所見，現場為距離龍脊山頂50米一塊空地，內有一座近1.7米高的疑似「魔爪」，外型貌似一隻只有3隻手指的動物枯乾前爪，爪的掌心刻上古怪符號，由木製成，表面塗有閃亮保護層。另外該建築由25條達1米高的木柱呈圓形包圍，地上更見兩盤建築用泥土、一條鐵支及一塊綠色帆布，疑有人於現場進行工程。<br />\n<br />\n記者到場發現，該空地觀景台位置已被漁護署人員用繩索及帆布封閉，並掛有請勿內進告示，指範圍內有工程正在進行。而觀景台內除了已被拆去的「魔爪」，仍有25條木柱，每條柱身鑽有孔洞，但未見有任何古怪文字符號或數字，疑用於駁上繩索用作圍欄。<br />\n<br />\n「魔爪」劣評如潮，據悉3日前被行山人士發現，今日即被拆除。今日早上有約7名工人登上龍脊拆除「魔爪」，不過合數人之力仍非常費勁，先移除上方爪部位置，再鋸斷底部金屬部份，最後要撬起底部石頭才可清除整個裝置。<br />\n<br />\n行山網民發現奇怪擺設後感不明所以，轟大殺風景「九唔搭八」，認為破壞自然景色，不願在山野看到人造建設，希望政府盡快拆走。另有網民推斷擺設與風水有關，認為非常邪門，「背脊生多隻手點會係好嘢」、「真係風水嘢，唔係好嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210308/VQL7RAQQH5BNPKJLT253BDCZXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210308%2FVQL7RAQQH5BNPKJLT253BDCZXE%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=2334f937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210308%2FVQL7RAQQH5BNPKJLT253BDCZXE%2F&h=ea8688e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210308/VQL7RAQQH5BNPKJLT253BDCZXE/</a>"},{"pid":"69bd5eb3a4251cee4e19c22e36c7b28658eda418","tid":2438381,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb4ddde88e3f19dd62742edd9f9961b6abcdeb4","tid":2438381,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abee14ef3034496746d66745f54cae78c9a0046","tid":2438381,"uid":8308,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"平時點會咁快拆"},{"pid":"575ebdbaf520c99d96b3502a6ddf572589295394","tid":2438381,"uid":45910,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"脈已斷，錢已袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4adb0e7e27d13b2a5ad26cbd769e69286b78ac","tid":2438381,"uid":179967,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:48:45.000Z","msg":"一睇就知拎黎洗黑錢 背後依單野又唔知洗幾多億<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74878a0db69ddca7661caee0c01cd531767fbaaf","tid":2438381,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"邪門野<br />\n<br />\n好學唔學"},{"pid":"f498d61fccc4e153ac0be3efb99a4b3e8b07eb12","tid":2438381,"uid":76804,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RHx0j5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RHx0j5.png&h=709db286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1457100/org/0cabf8047aea3a2d6bc8012e086d9f7a.jpeg/9XliA7m7sdC89rcwQpN3rBS165jhl_fhZFBsaWRQbGk?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1457100%2Forg%2F0cabf8047aea3a2d6bc8012e086d9f7a.jpeg%2F9XliA7m7sdC89rcwQpN3rBS165jhl_fhZFBsaWRQbGk%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=60f868f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1457106/org/0a424a2e53fc24b74cfa6c88ecf24d9b.jpeg/tcoJEg5FnXmkDnmEMyQFXtolHtAlOY-5L4irbC-Iq2w?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail